&lt;li&gt;Researches, analyzes, and documents findings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;May coach, review, and/or delegate work to other team members&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieves personal annual sales growth contract value based on the total opportunity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Achieves personal annual sales growth contract value based on the ability to both Sell-To and Sell&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;Through our existing customers (specific to Partner Sales)&lt;/li&gt;
