&lt;li&gt;Closes sales that meet the ConnectWise standards for pricing, margins, terms, and conditions (averages are subject to change based on segment, industry, product, etc.) o
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average size of transaction: $15K annual per sale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average number of sales: 85 transactions/year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Average length of sales cycle: 25-30 days&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
