&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Works collaboratively with sales executives to identify net-new sell-to opportunities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Heavy emphasis on outbound, proactive calling to cultivate business (75+ calls per day)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uses industry insights and ConnectWise value propositions to generate business leads via cold call, email, and social strategies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Uncovers business needs through a consultative approach to learn more about company objectives, pain points, processes, and opportunities for improvement&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drives sales growth and pipeline by setting up qualified meetings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identifies the appropriate opportunity for the correct solution, stays up to date on new software and products&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
